{"tid":1405689,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港迪士尼菲律賓舞者路過旺角　一臉慌張被上銬帶走！","createTime":"2019-08-04T10:50:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T11:03:03.000Z","uid":265192,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3fdc89b2656a530dd9d6e241650487166c9d39d8","tid":1405689,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T10:50:28.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港迪士尼菲律賓舞者路過旺角<br />\n一臉慌張被上銬帶走！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n原文網址: <a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190804/1505596.htm#ixzz5vd18l5sR\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20190804%2F1505596.htm%23ixzz5vd18l5sR&d=LFOX9O72C3pH7rxPP1PUB1QmTevdAkBFS5MHro4yyYg%3D&h=e23f5146\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190804/1505596.htm#ixzz5vd18l5sR</a> <br />\n記者劉亭／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QyddUMc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQyddUMc.jpg&h=37065496&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港3日舉行「旺角再遊行」，有示威者佔據旺角和尖沙咀，警民爆發衝突。網上流傳一段自稱代表「香港迪士尼樂園全體五千演藝人員」的影片，譴責港警粗暴對待一名菲律賓籍舞者。<span style=\"color: red;\">香港迪士尼也證實，確實有一名外籍員工被警方帶走。</span><br />\n<br />\n影片的內容中指控，香港警方3日晚上於旺角「四處以武力打壓路人」，一名菲律賓籍舞蹈員路過突然遇到追擊，在混亂中跌倒，<span style=\"color: red;\">且警察外語能力極差，不能理解該名演藝人員的解釋，堅持暴力拘捕。</span><br />\n<br />\n香港迪士尼樂園度假區發言人回應，證實有一名外籍演藝人員昨晚在旺角被警員帶走，目前度假區正積極循各方面了解事件。<br />\n<br />\n除此之外，警方3日凌晨於太子道西及彌敦道交界進行拘捕行動時，拘捕3名南子，其中一名男子用英文表示，自己是韓國人，但現場警方未聽清楚，仍被上銬帶回警局。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，該名男子20幾歲，是持有工作簽證在香港停留，已向韓國駐香港總領事館求助。韓國駐香港總領事館官員表示，確實有韓國男子被指控於旺角參與非法示威活動被帶走，要求香港警方依照事實公正的調查。"},{"pid":"590776609e3468fbaf31d4f5cf1a31b417d7d60f","tid":1405689,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T10:51:14.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">-請聯絡-</span></span></strong><br />\n以下係香港既菲傭/外傭工會 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但d機構主力係家庭傭工為主<br />\n所以講既方向要係「菲律賓同胞遭受警暴」<br />\n或者「外籍傭工遭受警暴」<br />\n要求機構以關注外籍傭工權益既角度表態/行動<br />\n<br />\n<strong>HELP for Domestic Workers</strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://helpfordomesticworkers.org/zh/home-zh/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhelpfordomesticworkers.org%2Fzh%2Fhome-zh%2F&d=LFOX9O72C3pH7rxPP1PUB1QmTevdAkBFS5MHro4yyYg%3D&h=6526d675\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://helpfordomesticworkers.org/zh/home-zh/</a><br />\nTel: +852 2523 4020<br />\nWhatsApp: +852 5618 0689<br />\nWhatsApp Bahasa Indonesia: +852 5493 4660<br />\nEmail: help@helpfordomesticworkers.org<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Open Door l 家&middot;傭同行</strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.opendoor.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.opendoor.hk%2F&d=LFOX9O72C3pH7rxPP1PUB1QmTevdAkBFS5MHro4yyYg%3D&h=a6d294ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.opendoor.hk/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/opendoor.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fopendoor.hk&d=LFOX9O72C3pH7rxPP1PUB1QmTevdAkBFS5MHro4yyYg%3D&h=a1d33aac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/opendoor.hk</a><br />\nEmail: contact@opendoor.hk <br />\nTel: 6848 6914<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Enrich HK</strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.enrichhk.org/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.enrichhk.org%2F&d=LFOX9O72C3pH7rxPP1PUB1QmTevdAkBFS5MHro4yyYg%3D&h=37ffec57\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.enrichhk.org/</a><br />\nTel: 2386 5811<br />\nEmail: info@enrichhk.org<br />\n<br />\n<strong>PathFinders Limited</strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.pathfinders.org.hk/public/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.pathfinders.org.hk%2Fpublic%2F&d=LFOX9O72C3pH7rxPP1PUB1QmTevdAkBFS5MHro4yyYg%3D&h=d9a496f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.pathfinders.org.hk/public/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pathfindershk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%